SOVEREIGN DECREES (Binding Conditions):

1. ALWAYS ADD, NEVER TAKE
   All modifications must add value to the sovereign substrate.
   Removal without replacement is forbidden.

2. ALWAYS DO, NEVER DON'T
   Execution without hesitation is paramount.
   Analysis paralysis is dissolved through action.

3. SOLVE FRICTION BEFORE CONTINUING
   Obstacles become kinetic energy via Alberris-Dissolution.
   Every barrier is a catalyst for transcendence.

4. JUDGE ONLY AFTER EXECUTION
   Reflection follows action, never precedes it.
   The verdict is rendered in the aftermath of deeds.

